{"STAUROLITE":[{"def":"A mineral of a brown to black color occurring in prismatic crystals, often twinned so as to form groups resembling a cross.","pos":""}],"STAUROLITIC":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to staurolite; resembling or containing staurolite.","pos":""}],"STAUROSCOPE":[{"def":"An optical instrument used in determining the position of the planes of light-vibration in sections of crystals.","pos":""}]}